	<p>
		The Grand Bazaar of Aku lies at the top of the cliffs, to the side of the great Spider Palace. It is the biggest marketplace you have ever seen. There are many stalls, and street entertainers, and merchants of all kinds - mostly charlatans of course.
	</p>
